09:27.567 --> 09:30.070
Yo, dingus, help me gaffle
some of these brews.

09:30.103 --> 09:32.305
Becca's being a cooze
and doesn't want me to drink

09:32.339 --> 09:33.974
so I actually pay attention.

09:34.007 --> 09:37.410
Anyway, pretend like you got
to go drop a dook,

09:37.444 --> 09:38.979
grab, like,
four of them dummies,

09:39.012 --> 09:40.480
leave 'em in the toilet tank
for me,

09:40.513 --> 09:42.082
Godfather-style.

09:42.115 --> 09:44.317
Nothing gets this pimp
through a dumb baby class

09:44.351 --> 09:45.619
like toilet beer.

09:45.653 --> 09:48.055
Hello, mommies and daddies.

09:48.088 --> 09:50.557
So, last week we covered
birth plans and how

09:50.590 --> 09:52.760
pretty much everyone poops
during labor.

09:52.793 --> 09:55.929
So today we're gonna practice
some real-life skills.

09:55.963 --> 09:58.598
Everybody come
and grab a baby doll. Come on.

09:58.632 --> 10:02.335
* Snuggle wuggle

10:02.369 --> 10:05.673
* Snuggle wuggle,
snuggle wuggle, snuggle wuggle *

10:05.706 --> 10:08.275
* Snuggle wuggle

10:08.308 --> 10:10.944
Emotions are dangerous,
Gretchen. Think about it,

10:10.978 --> 10:12.946
the most emotional
movie characters

10:12.980 --> 10:15.849
always die.
Kane from Citizen Kane.

10:15.883 --> 10:17.617
The wife from Up.

10:17.651 --> 10:20.988
Table-dancing destitute on
the bottom deck of the Titanic.

10:21.021 --> 10:23.123
And the ones
who survive in movies:

10:23.156 --> 10:25.859
RoboCop, Terminator,

10:25.893 --> 10:28.295
Chappie.
Those are all robots.

10:28.328 --> 10:29.963
Yeah, exactly. No emotions.

10:29.997 --> 10:32.933
Just cold circuitry
and a thirst for revenge.

10:32.966 --> 10:34.334
I don't really know
why you guys insist

10:34.367 --> 10:36.003
on sitting in
the backseat.

10:36.036 --> 10:37.437
I'm not an Uber.

10:37.470 --> 10:39.606
Yeah, damn right
you're not.

10:39.639 --> 10:40.440
(keys clacking)
What's that?

10:40.473 --> 10:41.842
His rating.

10:41.875 --> 10:43.176
(chime)

10:43.210 --> 10:46.346
(grunts)
One star.

10:46.379 --> 10:48.315
(sighs)

10:48.348 --> 10:51.451
Oh, almost forgot.
Give us your car booze.

10:51.484 --> 10:53.721
Guys, I really have to get
to my VA appointment.

10:53.754 --> 10:55.723
(whimpers)
(groans)
Fine.

10:55.756 --> 10:57.624
