with your stupid thing,

10:57.657 --> 10:58.859
you're giving us a ride home.

10:58.892 --> 11:02.029
(starts engine)

11:04.932 --> 11:06.900
Come on.
A little wah-wah,

11:06.934 --> 11:09.236
