then you're done.

11:09.269 --> 11:11.171
Pretend one of these
is your dad's grave.

11:11.204 --> 11:13.406
Yeah, the problem is
death doesn't bother me.

11:13.440 --> 11:15.675
I'm not upset
by the inevitable.

11:15.709 --> 11:17.677
It's like being upset
by the weather

11:17.711 --> 11:20.247
or by an Irishman
proving untrustworthy.

11:20.280 --> 11:21.849
(gasps)
Look.

11:21.882 --> 11:24.584
Real live dead person.

11:24.617 --> 11:27.755
Come on. Maybe it'll
stir something up.

11:27.788 --> 11:30.057
MINISTER:
...with so many questions
and so few answers.

11:30.090 --> 11:31.591
(quietly):
Hi. Sorry.

11:31.624 --> 11:33.026
But it would be a mistake
to think of today

11:33.060 --> 11:34.427
as a sad day.
(crying)

11:34.461 --> 11:35.695
Charlotte, if you would
please step forward.

11:40.400 --> 11:41.902
Our Father,
who art in heaven...

11:41.935 --> 11:45.672
Jimmy, am I...
Jimmy, am I crazy

11:45.705 --> 11:48.675
or is this funeral
hella sexy?

11:48.708 --> 11:51.678
I don't know
where that fetish came from,

11:51.711 --> 11:53.613
but it is absolutely...

11:56.984 --> 11:58.418
MINISTER:
...lead us not
into temptation...

11:58.451 --> 11:59.953
Oh, my God,
you're right.

11:59.987 --> 12:03.623
It's like the funeral
from November Rain.

12:03.656 --> 12:05.458
