24:17.724 --> 24:20.827
* That when your body
hit the earth *

24:22.394 --> 24:25.732
* It opened up
and swallowed you *

24:27.834 --> 24:31.370
* She kept you safe
in her heart's center *

24:31.403 --> 24:34.607
* And always tucked you in
at night *

24:34.641 --> 24:37.777
*

24:37.810 --> 24:40.212
* When you woke up nervous

24:41.914 --> 24:43.783
* She said, "Baby, you're..."

